OL,3,CRetired teacher with Crohn's says new
OL,4,Cresearch could be 'game-changer'
OL,6,FA retired primary school teacher who
OL,7,Fhas had four surgeries due to Crohn's
OL,8,Fdisease has said new research into the
OL,9,Fcondition could be a "complete game-
OL,10,Fchanger".
OL,12,FMaureen Dalgleish, 65, was first
OL,13,Fdiagnosed with Crohn's disease in
OL,14,F1988, aged 28.
OL,16,FSince then, she has surgery four times
OL,17,F` in 2001, 2006, 2013 and 2025 ` to
OL,18,Fmanage fibrosis in her bowel, related
OL,19,Fto the condition.
OL,26,@qD@VOUrD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
