PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1775523444
OL,3,CRetired teacher with Crohn's says new
OL,4,Cresearch could be 'game-changer'
OL,6,FShe has also spent long periods of her
OL,7,Flife on either a liquid diet or a
OL,8,Fheavily restricted diet, including
OL,9,Fafter surgery, to help manage symptoms.
OL,11,FBefore her most recent surgery she
OL,12,Fsuffered terrible abdominal pain and
OL,13,Fspasms, leading to nausea, fever,
OL,14,Fdizziness and even loss of
OL,15,Fconsciousness.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1775523444
OL,3,CRetired teacher with Crohn's says new
OL,4,Cresearch could be 'game-changer'
OL,6,FShe was invited to donate tissue from
OL,7,Fher surgery to the research led by a
OL,8,FUniversity of Edinburgh team and said
OL,9,Fshe was pleased to take part in the
OL,10,Fhope of helping others with the
OL,11,Fcondition.
OL,13,FThe 65-year-old, from Edinburgh, said:
OL,14,F"Before my surgery, I was in and out
OL,15,Fof hospital and it was incredibly
OL,16,Fexhausting. It can feel like your life
OL,17,Fis on hold.
OL,19,F"But I've learnt to plan my life
OL,20,Faround things and try not to let the
OL,21,Fcondition stop me.
OL,26,@vD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1775523444
OL,3,CRetired teacher with Crohn's says new
OL,4,Cresearch could be 'game-changer'
OL,6,F"The idea of having medication to
OL,7,Fcontrol or stop the fibrosis would be
OL,8,Famazing.
OL,10,F"Although I realise it probably won't
OL,11,Fbenefit me personally, this research
OL,12,Fcould potentially be a complete game-
OL,13,Fchanger for others like me. I wanted
OL,14,Fto get involved in the research to
OL,15,Fhelp them."
OL,17,FShe said she is really grateful to the
OL,18,F"marvellous team" at the Western
OL,19,FGeneral Hospital in Edinburgh who have
OL,20,Flooked after her.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@KO]zD@AOUzD@QO]
