PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1775523444
OL,3,CRetired teacher with Crohn's says new
OL,4,Cresearch could be 'game-changer'
OL,6,FThe retired teacher has noticed huge
OL,7,Fadvances in the diagnosis and
OL,8,Ftreatment of Crohn's in the decades
OL,9,Fshe has lived with it.
OL,11,FHowever it is understood surgery
OL,12,Fcurrently remains the only option to
OL,13,Fhelp with the fibrosis as after each
OL,14,Fsurgery to remove the damaged portion
OL,15,Fof the bowel, the disease re-starts
OL,16,Fand eventually the tissue becomes
OL,17,Fscarred again, leading to blockages.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/5
